 6. América-PE            1   8   0   1   7   8  22 -14
Obs.: 1) All teams refused to play against Flamengo in the first matches
(played from August to October). They alleged that Flamengo would be
eliminated in the Turno Eliminatório and could not play in Primeiro Turno.
      2) Flamengo didn't play in Segundo Turno.
